description: Wood-fired pizza made by Chef Fabio in our mobile oven.  Let Chef Fabio bring Italy to you!  Chef Fabio is a 3rd generation pizzaiolo from Domodossola, Italy.  The photo shows our setup at a recent private catering with our mobile, wood-fired pizza oven – also imported from Italy like Chef Fabio.  Our authentic, gourmet pizzas are made from scratch with the highest quality ingredients that are either imported from Italy or local and, ideally, organic following recipes that have been handed down from generation-to-generation.
name: Fabio On Fire LLC
